Module 6 â€“ Procedure Is Substance âš–ï¸ğŸ“œ
âš–ï¸ Core Message
Injustice often hides behind â€œmere procedure.â€ But for the unrepresented, procedure is the battlefield. Missing a step can mean losing the substance.

ğŸ“– Lesson Content
â€¢ Procedure as Gate ğŸšª â€” Courts use procedure to control access. If you donâ€™t meet the format, you donâ€™t get through the door.
â€¢ Procedure as Weapon ğŸ—¡ï¸ â€” Opposing counsel will exploit every missed deadline, misplaced exhibit, or defective certificate.
â€¢ Procedure as Protection ğŸ›¡ï¸ â€” Mastering procedure flips the script: it prevents dismissal and preserves your claims for review.
ğŸ“ Assignment
Take a procedural misstep youâ€™ve experienced (e.g., late filing, missing service certificate). Rewrite it into a correct, procedurally sound filing as if you could refile it today.

âœ… Model Answer (Example)
