1) **Transcript Order & Statement Regarding Issues** â€” identify all proceedings needed; if partial, include a short Statement of Issues.
2) **Designation of Appendix/Excerpts** â€” a oneâ€‘page table of contents listing every document, date, and ECF number youâ€™ll include.
3) **(Optional) Motion to Correct/Supplement Record** â€” if an exhibit or docket item is missing or misdescribed, draft a short motion under FRAP 10(e).

